OL,3,CCumbria Police uses specialist HGV as
OL,4,Cpart of road safety campaign
OL,6,FA five-day long operation by Cumbria
OL,7,FPolice has targeted drivers as part of
OL,8,Fa road safety campaign.
OL,10,FPolice used a specially equipped HGV
OL,11,Fto clamp down on the 'fatal four' -
OL,12,Fthe traffic offences which are a
OL,13,Fcommon factor in serious and deadly
OL,14,Froad traffic collisions.
OL,16,FThe 'fatal four' include speeding,
OL,17,Fusing a mobile phone behind the wheel,
OL,18,Fnot wearing a seatbelt and driving
OL,19,Funder the influence of drink or drugs.
