OL,3,CCumbria Police uses specialist HGV as
OL,4,Cpart of road safety campaign
OL,6,F"The majority of the offences
OL,7,Fidentified were people making a
OL,8,Fconscious decision to put their own
OL,9,Fwell-being and the well-being of other
OL,10,Froad users at risk ` from choosing to
OL,11,Freach for their phone whilst driving
OL,12,Fto making the decision to get behind
OL,13,Fthe wheel whilst disqualified.
OL,15,F"Cumbria Police, via its Roads
OL,16,FPolicing Unit, will continue to target
OL,17,Fsuch drivers as we work with our
OL,18,Fpartners to help make the county's
OL,19,Froads as safe as they can possibly be
OL,20,Ffor everyone."
